    "title": "Lead Investment Banker at New India Assurance Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Join the New India Assurance Advisory Limited family as a Investment Banker in Patna. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout New India Assurance Advisory Limited:\nNew India Assurance Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Income Tax\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Flexible working hours\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with New India Assurance Advisory Limited!",
